    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6389012>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Hyperaspis maindroni Sicard: a. nominate form; b. common variant; c. antenna; d. maxilla; e. labium; f. head; g. prosternum; h. abdomen, male; i. ventrite 6, female; j. abdominal postcoxal line (enlarged); k. coxites; l, m. spermatheca; n-s. male genitalia: n. tegmen, lateral view; o, r. tegmen, ventral view; p, s. penis; q, t. penis apex." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6389012/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6389016>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Hyperaspis sp. (Brazil) identified as H. maindroni Sicard: a–e. adult: a. dorsal view; b. ventral view; c. frontal view; d. rear view; e. lateral view; f. abdomen, male; g. ventrite 6, female; h–k. male genitalia: h. tegmen, lateral view; i. tegmen, ventral view; j. penis; k. penis apex; l, m, n. label data." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6389016/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6389020>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Life stages of H. maindroni Sicard: a–f. larva; g. pupa; h. adult." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6389020/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6389022>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. a–d. Larva of H. maindroni Sicard feeding on various mealybugs: a. solenopsis mealybug; b. cassava mealybug; c. Dysmicoccus brevipes (Cockerell); d. Ferrisia virgata (Cockerell); e–g. adult beetle in mealybug colony." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6389022/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6389026>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. a. Larvae of H. maindroni Sicard parasitized by Homalotylus turkmenicus Myartseva; b. larva with parasitoid emergence holes; c, d. Homalotylus turkmenicus, adult female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6389026/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6389028>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. a. Parasitized larva of H. maindroni Sicard; b, c. Metastenus concinnus Walker, adult female: b. dorsal view; c. lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6389028/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

